Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今日は何して遊ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:08.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}わかんない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:11.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おままごとは飽きちゃったしね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:12.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ね～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:17.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まだお母さんのお客さん帰らないのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:20.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早く帰っちゃえばいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:22.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なあに あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:40.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お人形が歩いてきたたの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:44.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すごく大きなお人形が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:51.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だか それは よくないもののような気がしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さん お母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:27.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あッ お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうは言うけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:30.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なことだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:32.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ええ でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:33.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:38.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン 部屋に入る時はノックしてって言ってるでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それと ご挨拶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:47.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いらっしゃいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:50.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失礼します お母様
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まあ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:55.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よろしい それで なあに？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}また不思議な虫でも見つけたの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でもお母様には見せないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:05.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虫じゃないよ お人形が歩いてきたの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:06.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お人形？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥様
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ご到着されました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:16.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ お人形 そういえば今日だったわね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:18.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居間にお通しして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:19.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}かしこまりました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:20.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}申し訳ありませんけど 続きはまた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:26.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}またって？この屋敷どうするの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの子一人で住むには…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:31.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから私たちが…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今日のところは お引き取りください
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:35.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ちょっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.62,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いい子にしててね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:57.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お待たせして ごめんなさい 遠いところ来てくれてありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}問題ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しゃべった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客様がお望みなら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どこでも駆けつけます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形サービス
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やっぱりお人形
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:10.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:13.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット·エヴァーガーデンです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さあ 今 お茶が入りますから かけていらして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:31.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お口に合うといいけれど どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}頂戴します
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飲んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飲んだ紅茶どうなるの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:40.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:45.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いずれ体から排出され 大地に返りますが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン 失礼ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}始めますか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:55.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私の貸出期間は7日間と承っております
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうね すぐ始めたいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}かしこまりました 作業はどちらでなさいますか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それじゃあ 明るいサンルームのほうでお願いしょうかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:08.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何するの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:11.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お手紙を書くのを手伝ってもらうのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お手紙なら私が書いてあげるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:17.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アンにはまだ難しい言葉は無理でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:18.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無理じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:25.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それにヴァイオレットさんはお手紙を書くのがとても上手で有名な方なの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰に書くの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:32.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうね とっても遠くにいる人よ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:33.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遠く？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:35.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:39.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なお手紙なの サンルームに入ってきてはダメよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:42.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それじゃヴァイオレットさん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:43.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}かしこまりました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こちらが持参したタイプライターになります
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:53.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それで大丈夫よ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:55.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}かしこまりました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やっぱりよくないものだったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すごい やっぱりお人形だわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥様
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さん 大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:27.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫よ すぐよくなるから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ホントに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:33.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ホントに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:38.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだ 私 子守歌 歌ってあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:43.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとう でもお母様は大人だから大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ 一緒に寝てもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:52.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もうお昼寝は卒業したでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今日はいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:59.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それよりアン お客様のお相手をしてさしあげて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客様は嫌い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:04.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私からお母さんを奪うんだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ごめんね アン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でもお願い 7日間だけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さんを困らせないで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母様は少しお休みになるんですって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:27.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さようですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ちょっと眠いだけですって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:37.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私があなたの相手をしてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客様は嫌いだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたはお人形だから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何をするのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:53.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうね お話しするとか何かして遊ぶとか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それは私の担当外の作業です
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ですが 少しの間でしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ お人形遊びするから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:06.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:17.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お人形がお人形で遊ぶなんて面白いでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これで何をすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:24.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お話ししたりお世話したりするに決まってるじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:25.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まず挨拶してみなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.62,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こんにちは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こんにちは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あら こんにちは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:40.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今のはお人形が言ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:44.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なるほど 理解しました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そっか あなたお人形だから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:50.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遊ばれたことはあっても遊んだことないのね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いえ 私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私が教えてあげるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それじゃあ 次はおままごとしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お庭にテーブルもあるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:03.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの お部屋の用意ができましたので ご案内いたします
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:04.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それでは お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}2階のお部屋になります
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何話してるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エリス
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私が持ってくわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:34.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いけません これはわたくしのお仕事ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}取らないでくださいまし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:43.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人生ってどうしてこうなのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:19.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私 アンよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうぞ お入りください
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうかなされましたか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何してるの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手を調整していたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}調整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい ちゃんと動くように
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ明日もお手紙書くの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:40.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その次の日も
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:46.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}7日だから その次の日も 次の日も
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:47.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:49.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰に書いてるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それは申し上げられません
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:53.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}守秘義務があるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しゅひ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:00.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難しい言葉ばかり使わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:02.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}申し訳ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お父様じゃないわよね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:07.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だってお父様はもういないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:10.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大きな戦争があったでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:13.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そこで立派な戦死を遂げられたの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ねえ 誰にお手紙書いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:22.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お嬢様 何かご用があっていらしたのでは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何かって…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:30.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エリスは帰っちゃったし お母さんはもうお休みになってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:37.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それではお嬢様 もうお休みになられては
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:39.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:42.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夜更かしは女性にとって大敵です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}カトレアさんがそう言っておられました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:47.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当社の別のドールです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:51.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別の？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.62,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:55.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他にもエリカさんとアイリスさんというドールが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:59.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すごいそんなに動くお人形がいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かったわ 寝るもん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:12.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたも寝ないとお母さんに怒られるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:16.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それに夜更かしすると いけないよオバケが出るんだからね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:21.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おやすみなさいませ お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:23.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おやすみ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}変なお人形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:49.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そしてその泥棒は 「わあ」と叫んで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ビックリして逃げていったのです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたなかなか本を読むの上手じゃない　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:04.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}パンはパンでも すごく硬くて食べられないパンってな~んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}スープに入れれば軟らかくなります
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:18.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さんが来るまでなぞなぞして 一緒に踊って おままごとして 虫をつかまえて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お嬢様 優先順位を教えてください
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットご本読んで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:27.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:35.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いかがでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ええ とってもいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ではこの印象で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:42.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:54.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ち 違うの ヴァ ヴァイオレットにリポンをつけてもらおうと思ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かったわ でもあとでね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:02.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥様 少しだけ体憩を頂いてもよろしいでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:06.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お嬢様は 今がよろしいのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}できましたよ お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:16.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当はヴァイオレットにリボンをつけてほしいんじゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:17.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:20.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当はお母さんにしてほしいの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:22.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:26.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一緒にご本読むのも なぞなぞも おままごとも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虫はお母さん苦手だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さんと私の時間を取らないでヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あと数日です
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:40.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ手紙を書いている時 私もそばにいていいって言って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}近くにいたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そばにいて手をギュッテて握るだけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:50.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}申し訳ありません 承りかねます
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:51.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すみません お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:56.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そろそろ戻らなくてはいけません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今日中にいけそうかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:08.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい この調子であれば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥様 お願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:13.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥様
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:15.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫よ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥様
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:23.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫よ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:24.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しかし
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お願い 続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もうやめて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さん もうやめて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:36.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン 大丈夫だから 向こうへ行っててちょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:42.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして どうして手紙を書くの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰に書くの お父さんはもういないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事な手紙なの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:50.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私が知らない誰かの手紙何でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お見舞いも来ない誰かよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:58.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さんのことを本当に心配している人なんていないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私より大事な手紙なの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アンより大事なものなんてないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さんはウソばっかり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ウソじゃないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:22.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だってお母さんちっともよくならないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:24.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すぐに元気になるって言ったくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:25.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:29.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私知ってる お母さんは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:33.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さんがいなくなったら 私1人よ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私はいつまでお母さんと一緒にいられるの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:45.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これからずっと1人になるなら 手紙なんて書くかないで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今私と一緒にいて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:50.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私といてよ お母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:54.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:00.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:39.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お嬢様の時間を 私が消費していることには意味があります
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:43.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうかお母様に対してお怒りにならないでください
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だって だって…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:49.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お嬢様がおつらいのは当たり前です
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:54.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その小さな体で すでにお母様のご病気を受け止めていらっしゃる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたはとても立派です
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}立派じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:02.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}立派じゃない…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さんを泣かせちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:11.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいえ お嬢様はお優しい方です
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:12.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}違う…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:13.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}違う
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}違う 違う
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:22.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私がイヤな子だから お母さんが病気になって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}関係ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}違う 違う 違う
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:30.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰にもどうにもならないことなのです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}違う
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:33.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私の腕があなたの腕のように
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:39.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}柔らかい肌にはならないのと同じくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:44.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしよもないことなのです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:55.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さん…お母さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして手紙を書くの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人には届けたい想いがあるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:09.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんなの 届かなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:18.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}届かなくていい手紙なんて ないのですよ お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:36.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして 私を抱きしめてくれたお人形が手紙を書き終えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:38.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さよならする日が来た
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:50.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:01.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:02.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あったかい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:11.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もしかして…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:15.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それじゃ飲んだ紅茶は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:21.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ですから いずれ体内から排出され 大地に返ります
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:30.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それはお人形じゃなかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:34.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それからよくないものでもなかったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}とっても優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:43.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私あの人が書いた手紙読んでみたかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一体誰への手紙だったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:48.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さあ お茶にしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:55.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さんお人形遊びをしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:56.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:00.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それから ご本読んでおままごとして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まあまあ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:13.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:19.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私のアン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:47.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:57.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン 8歳の誕生日おめでとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:21:59.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}悲しいことがたくさんあるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:03.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}頑張ることが多くてくじけているかも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:04.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも負けないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:08.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寂しくて泣いてしまうこともあるかもしれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:10.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忘れないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:14.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母さんはいつもアンのこと愛してるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:21.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン 10歳の誕生日おめでとう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:25.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}背も伸びて ずいぶん大きくなったんでしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:29.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でもまだ本を読むのと 踊ることは好きでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:33.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なぞなぞと虫取りは卒業したかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:39.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}18歳の誕生日おめでとう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:41.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう立派なレディーね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:44.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好きな人ができたかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:47.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恋の相談には乗れないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:53.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたが選ぶ人ならきっと とてもステキな人よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:01.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誕生日おめでとう アン
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:05.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}20年も生きたのね すごいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:09.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大人になっても たまには弱音を吐いてもいいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:13.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたが不安になっても 私がいるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:17.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アン
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:21.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.74,0:23:22.62,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:25.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見守ってるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.18,0:23:47.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お疲れさま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:49.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すごい量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:54.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今後50年にわたって アン·マグノリアに届ける手紙です
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.59,0:23:55.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}50通も書いたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:24:00.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久しぶりの出張代筆だったのに大丈夫だった
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:02.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}問題ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:03.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも ステキね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:06.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これから毎年届くのが楽しみね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.60,0:24:09.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい ですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.73,0:24:17.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}届く頃には お母様は…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.57,0:24:18.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まだ あんなに小さい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:21.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寂しがり屋で…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:26.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お母様が大好きなお嬢様を残して
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.11,0:24:31.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あのお屋敷に1人残されて…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.53,0:24:33.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.87,0:24:43.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私お屋敷ではずっと泣くのを我慢していました
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.06,0:24:47.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でもヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:52.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}届くのよ あなたの書いた手紙が
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.30,0:25:00.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それに 遠く離れていても
Comment: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,ch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:08.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:11.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}過家家都玩膩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:12.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:17.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}媽媽的客人還不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:20.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要是早點回去就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:22.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:40.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}人偶走過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:44.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一個超級大的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:51.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}總感覺 那不是個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:27.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:30.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可這事情很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:32.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:33.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:38.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮 不是跟你說過進房間前要敲門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還有 快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:47.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:50.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}失禮了 母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:55.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很好 那麼有什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}又發現了不可思議的蟲子麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不過別給媽媽看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:05.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是蟲子 有人偶走過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:06.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:16.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}人偶啊 說起來就是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:18.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}帶她去客廳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:19.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:20.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}十分抱歉 我們下次再說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:26.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}下次？這棟房子要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}讓那孩子一個人住也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:31.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以我們才…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天就請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:35.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.62,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要做個好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:57.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉讓您久等了 感謝您遠道而來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要客人有要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不論身在何處 都能為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是自動手記人偶服務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}果然是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:10.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:13.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特·伊芙加登
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我這就去給您倒茶 請坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:31.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不知是否合您口味 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喝下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喝下去的紅茶會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:40.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:45.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}之後會從體內排出 回歸大地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮 這樣很沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:55.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的租借時限是七天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 我想馬上開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白了 請問在哪裡工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那就在明亮的日光室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:08.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:11.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她要幫我寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要寫信的話我可以幫你寫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:17.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮還不會用複雜的詞語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:18.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:25.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且 薇爾莉特小姐擅長寫信是出了名的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要寫給誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:32.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 要寫給很遙遠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:33.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}遙遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:35.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:39.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是很重要的信 你不要進日光室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:42.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好了 薇爾莉特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:43.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這是我自己帶的打字機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:53.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:55.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}果然不是什麼好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好厲害 果然她是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}媽媽 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:27.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒事哦 一會兒就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:33.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:38.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}對了 我給你唱搖籃曲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:43.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}謝謝你 不過媽媽是大人了 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那可以一起睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:52.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是已經不午睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天就算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:59.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}比起這個 安妮 去陪陪客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不喜歡客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:04.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是她把媽媽搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}對不起 安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不過拜託了 就這七天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要讓媽媽為難哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}母親大人要稍微休息會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:27.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她說她只是有點睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:37.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我來陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}雖然我討厭客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但你是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:53.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想想 聊聊天 或者玩點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這是我職責外的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不過 只是一會兒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那我們玩人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:06.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:17.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}人偶玩人偶 很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這個要怎麼玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:24.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}當然是跟她說說話 照顧她啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:25.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}先和她打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.62,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哎呀 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:40.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}剛才那句是人偶說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:44.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}原來如此 我理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我懂了 因為你是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:50.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以就算被玩過 但也不知道怎麼玩對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我來教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}接下來玩過家家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}庭院裡有桌子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:03.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那個 房間已經準備好了 我帶您過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:04.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那麼大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}房間在二樓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}讓我去送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:34.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不行 這是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}請不要搶我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:43.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}人生為什麼總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:19.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我在調整手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}調整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的 為了讓它能正常活動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那明天你也要寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:40.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}後面那天也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:46.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}七天的話 後面的後面那天也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:47.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:49.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}寫給誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:53.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因為我有保密的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}保密…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:00.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要老是用複雜的詞語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:02.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是寫給父親的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:07.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因為父親大人已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:10.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是有場很大的戰爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:13.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他在那裡英勇犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}問你 是寫給誰的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:22.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大小姐 您有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:30.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}艾莉絲回去了 媽媽也睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:37.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那麼大小姐 您也去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:39.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:42.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}熬夜對女性不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嘉德麗雅小姐這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:47.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是本公司的另一位人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:51.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}另一位？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.62,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:55.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}另外還有叫艾麗卡和愛麗絲的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:59.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好厲害 有這麼多能動的人偶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我知道啦 去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:12.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你也是 不睡的話媽媽會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:16.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還有 不能熬夜不然妖怪會出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:21.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}晚安 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:23.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這人偶真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:49.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然後那個小偷「哇」得叫了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嚇得逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你還挺擅長念書的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:04.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是麵包但硬到不能吃的是什麼麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}泡在湯裡就軟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特 薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:18.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在媽媽來之前我們一起猜謎 跳舞 過家家 捉蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大小姐 請告訴我優先順序
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特 給我念書聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:27.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特 薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:35.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那就按這個感覺來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:42.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:54.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是的 我是想讓薇爾莉特幫我繫髮帶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我知道了 但先等等好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:02.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夫人 我能稍微休息一兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:06.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大小姐 現在就系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:16.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}其實我不是想讓薇爾莉特幫我繫髮帶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:17.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:20.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}其實我想讓媽媽幫我繫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:22.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:26.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還有一起看書 猜謎語 過家家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}雖然媽媽不喜歡蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}別搶走我和媽媽相處的時間 薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就剩幾天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:40.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那你能跟她說嗎 至少寫信的時候讓我待在邊上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想在她身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只是在邊上牽住她的手就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:50.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}非常抱歉 我不能答應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:51.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}對不起 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:56.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天之內能完成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:08.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}照這個狀態的話 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夫人 請看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:13.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:15.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:23.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:24.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}拜託你 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\an8}大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}媽媽 快停下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:36.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮 我沒事的 你出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:42.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}為什麼 為什麼還要寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這是給誰寫的 爸爸已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這是很重要的信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:50.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}反正是寫給我不認識的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那人一次都沒有探望過你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:58.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明沒人真擔心媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這封信比我還重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒有什麼比安妮更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}媽媽淨會說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我沒有說謊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:22.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是媽媽一點也沒好轉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:24.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明說過很快就會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:25.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:29.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我知道的 媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:33.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要是媽媽不在的話 就只剩我一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我還能和媽媽在一起多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:45.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果以後只剩我一人 就別寫信了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}趁現在陪陪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:50.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}陪在我身邊啊 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:54.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:00.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:39.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我現在消耗大小姐和夫人相處的時間是有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:43.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}請您不要對母親發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:49.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大小姐感到痛苦 這很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:54.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您這麼小 卻已接受了母親的病情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您非常了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒什麼了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:02.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒什麼了不起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}讓媽媽哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:11.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 大小姐很善良
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:12.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:13.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}才不是 才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:22.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因為我是壞孩子 媽媽才會生病
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是 不是 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:30.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這件事 誰都沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:33.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就像我的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:39.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}無法變得像你的雙手那般柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:44.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:55.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}媽媽…媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}為什麼還要寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因為有想要傳達給某人的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:09.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那種東西 用不著傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:18.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不存在無需傳達的書信 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:36.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}後來 抱著我的人偶寫完了信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:38.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到了告別的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:50.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:01.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:02.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}暖乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:11.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:15.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那喝下去的紅茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:21.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我說過了 之後會排出體外 回歸大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:30.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她不是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:34.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也不是什麼壞東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她非常溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:43.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我好想看看她寫的信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這封信到底是寫給誰的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:48.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}來喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:55.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}媽媽 來玩人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:56.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:00.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還有一起念書 過家家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:13.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:19.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:47.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:57.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮 八歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:21:59.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也許你會經歷很多悲傷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:03.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也許努力過後仍遭遇挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:04.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是別放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:08.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有時會很寂寞 會哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:10.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:14.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}媽媽永遠愛著安妮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:21.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮 十歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:25.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想必你應該長高了 長大不少
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:29.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但應該還喜歡讀書和跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:33.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是不是不再玩猜謎語和捉蟲子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:39.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}十八歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:41.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你已經長成一名出色的女性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:44.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有心上人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:47.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}雖然媽媽不能給你戀愛上的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:53.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但你所選擇的人一定很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:01.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}生日快樂 安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:05.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你已經生活了二十年了 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:09.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}即使長大成人 偶爾也能說洩氣話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:13.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}即便你感到不安 也還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:17.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安妮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:21.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我會永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.74,0:23:22.62,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:25.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}永遠守護著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.18,0:23:47.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:49.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:54.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這是今後分五十年寄給安妮·馬格諾利亞的信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.59,0:23:55.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}足足寫了五十封嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:24:00.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你好久沒出差代筆寫信了 吃得消嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:02.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:03.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}話說回來 真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:06.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今後每年都好期待把信寄出去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.60,0:24:09.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.73,0:24:17.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}信件送達的時候 母親已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.57,0:24:18.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明她還那麼小
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:21.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怕寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:26.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}把最愛媽媽的大小姐留下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.11,0:24:31.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一個人留在那間宅邸裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.53,0:24:33.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.87,0:24:43.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我在那裡一直忍住沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.06,0:24:47.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不過薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:52.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你寫的信 會送到的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.30,0:25:00.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且 縱使兩人相隔千里
