Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:15.70,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}難以領悟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.29,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一句「再見」傷感不已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:27.35,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一聲「愛你」遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:35.44,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}這份思念無法言喻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:42.76,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}讓人惶恐    卻又無比令人憐惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:49.02,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}我眼中的淚 到底為何而流
