Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:08.74,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}埋藏在心裡    一句又一句
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:17.58,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}我止不住地想見到你
