Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.40,0:25:38.53,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一隻小鳥 婉轉鳴叫著
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.18,0:25:49.59,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}在未知的天空中 四處尋找我
